					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">VRC6 and N163 would have supported up to 256KiB and 32KiB of RAM for nametables respectively (both in lieu of the in-NES NTRAM), and N163 supported swapping that RAM around between tile data and nametable data.<br /><br />It would also be easy to add a 74'139 to convert <em>any</em> ASIC mapper to allow for ROM nametables and NTRAM-as-CHRRAM.</div>

